  "core_title": {
    "en": "New Friends at the Café",
    "ja": "カフェでできた新しい友だち",
    "fr": "De nouveaux amis au café",
    "ko": "카페에서 만난 새로운 친구들"
  },
  "core_reading_html": {
    "en": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-hello' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"hello\", \"vocab-hello\")'>Hello</span></strong>! My name is Emma. I am a <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-student' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"student\", \"vocab-student\")'>student</span></strong> from Egypt. I live in a small <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-flat' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"flat\", \"vocab-flat\")'>flat</span></strong> with my family. Today I meet a new <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-friend' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"friend\", \"vocab-friend\")'>friend</span></strong> at a <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-cafe' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"cafe\", \"vocab-cafe\")'>café</span></strong>. We talk about our <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-name' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"name\", \"vocab-name\")'>names</span></strong>, families, and cities. We order <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-food' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"food\", \"vocab-food\")'>food</span></strong> and a cold <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-drink' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"drink\", \"vocab-drink\")'>drink</span></strong>. The <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-server' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"server\", \"vocab-server\")'>server</span></strong> is very kind. Before we leave, we check a <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-phone' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"phone\", \"vocab-phone\")'>phone</span></strong> number and say, 'Goodbye! See you soon!'</p>",
    "ja": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-konnichiwa' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"konnichiwa\", \"vocab-konnichiwa\")'>こんにちは</span></strong>。私はエマです。私はエジプトから来た<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-gakusei' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"gakusei\", \"vocab-gakusei\")'>学生</span></strong>です。家族と小さな<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-apato' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"apato\", \"vocab-apato\")'>アパート</span></strong>に住んでいます。今日はカフェで新しい<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-tomodachi' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"tomodachi\", \"vocab-tomodachi\")'>友だち</span></strong>に会いました。私たちは<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-kafe' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"kafe\", \"vocab-kafe\")'>カフェ</span></strong>で名前や家族、町について話しました。そして<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-namae' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"namae\", \"vocab-namae\")'>名前</span></strong>を紹介し、<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-tabemono' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"tabemono\", \"vocab-tabemono\")'>食べ物</span></strong>と冷たい<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-nomimono' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"nomimono\", \"vocab-nomimono\")'>飲み物</span></strong>を注文しました。<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-tenin' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"tenin\", \"vocab-tenin\")'>店員</span></strong>さんはとても親切でした。帰る前に<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-denwa' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"denwa\", \"vocab-denwa\")'>電話</span></strong>番号を確認して、「またね！」と言いました。</p>",
    "fr": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-bonjour' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"bonjour\", \"vocab-bonjour\")'>Bonjour</span></strong> ! Je m'appelle Emma. Je suis une <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-etudiante' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"etudiante\", \"vocab-etudiante\")'>étudiante</span></strong> d'Égypte. J'habite dans un petit <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-appartement' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"appartement\", \"vocab-appartement\")'>appartement</span></strong> avec ma famille. Aujourd'hui, je rencontre une nouvelle <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-amie' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"amie\", \"vocab-amie\")'>amie</span></strong> dans un <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-cafe' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"cafe\", \"vocab-cafe\")'>café</span></strong>. Nous parlons de nos <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-nom' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"nom\", \"vocab-nom\")'>noms</span></strong>, de nos familles et de nos villes. Nous commandons de la <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-nourriture' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"nourriture\", \"vocab-nourriture\")'>nourriture</span></strong> et une <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-boisson' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"boisson\", \"vocab-boisson\")'>boisson</span></strong> froide. Le <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-serveur' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"serveur\", \"vocab-serveur\")'>serveur</span></strong> est très gentil. Avant de partir, nous vérifions un numéro de <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-telephone' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"telephone\", \"vocab-telephone\")'>téléphone</span></strong> et nous disons : « Au revoir ! À bientôt ! »</p>",
    "ko": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-annyeonghaseyo' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"annyeonghaseyo\", \"vocab-annyeonghaseyo\")'>안녕하세요</span></strong>! 제 이름은 엠마입니다. 저는 이집트에서 온 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-haksaeng' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"haksaeng\", \"vocab-haksaeng\")'>학생</span></strong>입니다. 가족과 작은 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-apateu' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"apateu\", \"vocab-apateu\")'>아파트</span></strong>에 살고 있습니다. 오늘 저는 카페에서 새로운 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-chingu' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"chingu\", \"vocab-chingu\")'>친구</span></strong>를 만났습니다. 우리는 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-kape' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"kape\", \"vocab-kape\")'>카페</span></strong>에서 이름과 가족, 사는 도시에 대해 이야기했습니다. 그리고 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-ireum' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"ireum\", \"vocab-ireum\")'>이름</span></strong>을 소개하고 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-eumsik' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"eumsik\", \"vocab-eumsik\")'>음식</span></strong>과 차가운 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-eumryo' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"eumryo\", \"vocab-eumryo\")'>음료</span></strong>를 주문했습니다. <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-jigwon' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"jigwon\", \"vocab-jigwon\")'>직원</span></strong>은 매우 친절했습니다. 집에 가기 전에 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-jeonhwa' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"jeonhwa\", \"vocab-jeonhwa\")'>전화</span></strong>번호를 확인하고 “안녕! 또 만나!”라고 말했습니다.</p>"
  },
